Website: [url=http://daftx.ucoz.com/]http://daftx.ucoz.com/[/url] Webclient: [url=http://daftx.ucoz.com/index/webclient/0-4]http://daftx.ucoz.com/index/webclient/0-4[/url] Forums: [url=http://daftx.ucoz.com/forum]http://daftx.ucoz.com/forum[/url] Client.jar: [url=https://www.dropbox.com/s/agb0a8ksghctc7h/DaftXV1.jar]https://www.dropbox.com/s/agb0a8ksghctc7h/DaftXV1.jar[/url] Client.rar: [url=https://www.dropbox.com/s/xaprr3b0km4s8kh/DaftX%20Real%20Client.rar]https://www.dropbox.com/s/xaprr3b0km4s8kh/DaftX%20Real%20Client.rar[/url]
Features: 100% overloads
Very daily updates(I'm open to any suggestions and critism.)
100% slayer helm and black mask to make slayer more popular, also there's elite tasks which are mostly bosses that will make wearing black mask/slayer helmet very useful.
Very smooth combat, drop rates are hard but not too hard.
Request help system
Teleport to task option from slayer master to skip past the teleporting and walking to tasks.
All skills have a purpose and there's a economy for things like making armour, fishing, and herblore.
Pics Wise old man, teleports you to one of his triplets, whom he named them all max [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/wise_zps5aa709b1.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/wise_zps5aa709b1.png[/img][/URL]

[URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/DaftXMAX_zps5c430219.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/DaftXMAX_zps5c430219.png[/img][/URL]
[b]Custom boss max (range) [/b] [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/range_zpsc0b86c71.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/range_zpsc0b86c71.png[/img][/URL]
[b]Custom boss max (mage) [/b] [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/mage_zpse7852f5b.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/mage_zpse7852f5b.png[/img][/URL]
[b]Cozar's rapier, custom rapier that hits as fast as range knives and is dropped by cozar the legendary[/b] [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/Untitled_zps8df0fc4d.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/Untitled_zps8df0fc4d.png[/img][/URL]
[b]Cozar the legendary [/b] [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/Untitled2_zps8c89c582.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/Untitled2_zps8c89c582.png[/img][/URL]
Flawless Korasi Special Attack [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/KORASI_zps9f05cebf.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/KORASI_zps9f05cebf.png[/img][/URL]
Offhands added but speculating on how they will function [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/offhands_zps087aae9b.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/offhands_zps087aae9b.png[/img][/URL]
Staff tab [URL=http://s1317.photobucket.com/user/strverylow/media/tab_zps51edf401.png.html][IMG]http://i1317.photobucket.com/albums/t637/strverylow/tab_zps51edf401.png[/img][/URL]
Other features are fully working curses, fully working godwars, corporal beast coded in 100%, etc. Come check out the server, I promise you won't regret.
